content.rendered:
Directed by Shantanu Bagchi

Written by Parveez Sheikh. Aseem Arrora. Sumit Batheja

Cast Rashmika Mandanna. Sidharth Malhotra. Kumud Mishra. Sharib Hashmi. Parmeet Sethi(R. N. Kao). Awlad Hossen Eshan((credit only)). Mir Sarwar. Rukh Nabeel. Zachary Coffin (Isaac Mossad Chief). Iamrealmohsin (Aslam Worker).Kartik Srivastava. Sharik Khan (Avni’s friend). Sunny Yadav. Mohd Talib. Neel Vishal Mishra. Ariyan Mehedi. Vikram Sharma(ISI Agent). Bikram Malati(Parbhu). Anaya Kashyap. DJ Virus. Pyarali Nayani(Barbar – Saleem Khan). Mukesh Fotwani(Guard in the train). Inzmam(ISI Agent). Arvind Jangid(Commando). Gajendra Pratap Singh(ISI Agent). Zohab Khan(I.s.i agent). Gunjan Sinha(Ali). Rabiat Baysoltanovna Osaeva(Mr. Khan’s wife). Praveen Gaur(Mohd Rafeeq)

Language Hindi

Producers Amar Butala. Arun Singh Dikky. Alex Anthony Fernandes. Hasanain Hooda. Pashan Jal. Garima Mehta. Mukesh Prajapati. Ronnie Screwvala. Arif Shaikh. Meraj Shaikh. Sukruth Sudhakar.

Production 88 Pictures. GBA Media. RSVP
